<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: lightgray;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }

        .character {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

            .character img {
                width: 200px;
                height: 200px;
                border-radius: 50%;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

        .character-details {
            text-align: center;
        }

            .character-details h2 {
                font-size: 24px;
                margin: 10px 0;
                color: #007bff;
            }

            .character-details p {
                font-size: 16px;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
                color: #666;
                line-height: 1.6;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>About Us</h1>

        <!-- Khumalo -->
        <div class="character">
            <img src="~/Images/tech-product.jpg" alt="Khumalo">
            <div class="character-details">
                <h2>Khumalo</h2>
                <p>Founder & CEO</p>
                <p>Khumalo is the visionary entrepreneur who founded KhumaloCraft Emporium. With a passion for connecting artisans worldwide, he leads the team towards realizing the dream of showcasing handcrafted products to a global audience.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        
        <div class="character">
            <img src="~/Images/istockphoto-1254942778-612x612.jpg" alt="Aryan Lutchminarian">
            <div class="character-details">
                <h2>Aryan Lutchminarian</h2>
                <p>Artisan Liaison</p>
                <p>Aryan Lutchminarian plays a key role in liaising with artisans from around the world, ensuring that their craftwork is showcased on the platform. They work closely with Khumalo to curate a diverse selection of handcrafted products.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        
        <div class="character">
            <img src="~/Images/Depositphotos_19288743_youngbusinessman.jpg" alt="Mikyle Gounden">
            <div class="character-details">
                <h2>Mikyle Gounden</h2>
                <p>Marketing Specialist</p>
                <p>Mikyle Gounden is responsible for promoting KhumaloCraft Emporium to a global audience. Through strategic marketing campaigns and initiatives, they raise awareness about the platform and attract customers who appreciate artisanal craftsmanship.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        
        <div class="character">
            <img src="~/Images/istockphoto-1453312317-170667a.jpg" alt="Lethabo Mashilo">
            <div class="character-details">
                <h2>Lethabo Mashilo</h2>
                <p>Customer Experience Manager</p>
                <p>Lethabo Mashilo ensures that customers have a seamless and enjoyable shopping experience on KhumaloCraft Emporium. They oversee customer support, feedback management, and implement strategies to enhance customer satisfaction.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
